
NOTES FROM THE YOUTUBE VIDEO:

-Image classification: is a concept that consists on classifying images based on predefined categories
-used Technology: python library scikit learn
-input= image; output= image category
-confidence score: a float value between 0 and 1, it is returned with the image caegory.
-Metrics: confusion matrix (summerises performance), accuracy, precision and recall.

HOW TO MAKE AN IMAGE CLASSIFIER:

-sckikit-learn library: https://scikit-learn.org/stable/install.html
-two datasets: pictures that show accidents and pictures that show a normal traffic flow.
